    • JavaFile

      public JavaFile(String location, String packageName, String name, int coupling, int lines)
      Parameters:
      location - is the absolute location of the file in the hard drive
      packageName - is the name of the package that will be found after reading inside java file
      name - is the name of the file without its ext
      coupling - is the count of intern and extern coupling found using Icsec
      lines - is the count of lines found using nvloc
